213
00:29:24,285 --> 00:29:27,286
<font color="yellow">-Attention, Louis.</font>

214
00:29:27,286 --> 00:29:32,885
<font color="yellow">Louis !</font>

215
00:29:45,080 --> 00:29:53,414
<font color="yellow">-145, pied au plancher, quel veau!
