239
00:31:46,993 --> 00:31:50,868
<font color="white">A votre service.</font>

240
00:31:50,868 --> 00:31:56,411
<font color="green">Propos en allemand.</font>

241
00:31:56,411 --> 00:32:01,120
<font color="white">-Tavernier,
