325
00:38:40,010 --> 00:38:43,052
<font color="white">Tavernier !</font>

326
00:38:43,052 --> 00:38:48,521
<font color="red">Elle rit.</font>

327
00:39:01,929 --> 00:39:04,388
<font color="white">-Viens te coucher...</font>

328
00:39:04,388 --> 00:39:09,410
<font color="white">Julien Tavernier.</font>

329
00:39:09,410 --> 00:39:16,442
<font color="red">Battement de la pluie</font>

