00:39:33,559 --> 00:39:36,434
<font color="cyan">-JuHen….</font>

331
00:39:36,434 --> 00:39:39,893
<font color="cyan">Je t'aurai cherché partout.</font>

332
00:39:39,893 --> 00:39:46,274
<font color="red">Coup de tonnerre</font>

