00:40:23,212 --> 00:40:28,811
<font color="red">Grincement</font>

334
00:43:11,590 --> 00:43:19,924
<font color="magenta">Extrait de la bande originale</font>

335
00:45:55,779 --> 00:45:58,238
<font color="white">-Bonsoir, madame.
</font><font color="yellow">-Bonsoh.</font>

336
00:45:58,238 --> 00:46:03,260
<font color="white">-Auriez-vous vu Julien, ce soir ?
