344
00:47:04,539 --> 00:47:06,935
<font color="cyan">Il faut...</font>

345
00:47:06,935 --> 00:47:09,290
<font color="cyan">Il faut...</font>

346
00:47:09,290 --> 00:47:10,665
<font color="yellow">-Dites…
</font><font color="cyan">-II faut...</font>

347
00:47:10,665 --> 00:47:14,832
<font color="white">-On se connaît.
Christian Subervie.</font>

348
00:47:14,832 --> 00:47:18,520
<font color="white">Je suis un pote de Julien.
