576
01:10:37,739 --> 01:10:43,323
<font color="white">-C'est marrant, il ferme jamais.</font>

577
01:10:43,323 --> 01:10:48,678
<font color="white">Oh dis donc!</font>

578
01:10:48,678 --> 01:10:51,199
<font color="white">Dis donc...</font>

579
01:10:51,199 --> 01:10:54,220
<font color="white">Mais alors...</font>

580
01:10:54,220 --> 01:10:58,637
<font color="white">Oh dis donc...</font>

581
01:10:58,637 --> 01:11:03,034
<font color="yellow">Hé, la police.
