01:21:16,683 --> 01:21:21,329
<font color="magenta">Quelqu'un joue du piano.</font>

707
01:21:21,329 --> 01:21:25,163
<font color="yellow">-Mets ton manteau, Claudine.</font>

708
01:21:25,163 --> 01:21:28,518
<font color="white">-AHons,dépéchons,
